<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 80px; margin-right: 15px;">
                ລົດມືສອງຄຸນນະພາບ
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">ໜ້າຫຼັກ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/sell-car">ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">ຕິດຕໍ່</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/login">ແອດມິນ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
            <div class="card-header bg-gold text-dark">
                <h2>ສະເໜີຂາຍລົດ</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <% if (error) { %>
                    <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                        <%- error %>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                <% if (success) { %>
                    <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                        <%- success %>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                <form action="/sell-car" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ຊື່ຜູ້ຂາຍ</label>
                        <input type="text" name="sellerName" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ເບີໂທ</label>
                        <input type="text" name="phone" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ຍີ່ຫໍ້</label>
                        <select name="brand" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="">ເລືອກຍີ່ຫໍ້</option>
                            <option value="Toyota">Toyota</option>
                            <option value="Honda">Honda</option>
                            <option value="Mazda">Mazda</option>
                            <option value="Mitsubishi">Mitsubishi</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ລຸ້ນ</label>
                        <input type="text" name="model" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ປີ</label>
                        <input type="number" name="year" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ລາຄາ</label>
                        <input type="number" name="price" class="form-control" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ເກຍ</label>
                        <select name="transmission" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="Automatic">ອັດຕະໂນມັດ</option>
                            <option value="Manual">ຄູ່ມື</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ໄມລ໌</label>
                        <input type="number" name="mileage" class="form-control" placeholder="ກິໂລແມັດ">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ລາຍລະອຽດ</label>
                        <textarea name="description" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="ລາຍລະອຽດລົດ"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ແຂວງ</label>
                        <select name="province" class="form-control" required>
                            <% provinces.forEach(province => { %>
                                <option value="<%- province %>"><%- province %></option>
                            <% }) %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ຮູບພາບ (ສູງສຸດ 10 ຮູບ)</label>
                        <input type="file" name="images" class="form-control" multiple>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ເລືອກຮູບປົກ</label>
                        <input type="number" name="coverImageIndex" class="form-control" min="0" max="9" placeholder="ດັດສະນີຮູບ (0-9)">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ສະຖານະການກວດສອບ</label>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="noFlood" id="noFlood" checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="noFlood">ບໍ່ເຄີຍຖືກນໍ້າຖ້ວມ</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="noMajorAccident" id="noMajorAccident" checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="noMajorAccident">ບໍ່ເຄີຍປະສົບອຸປະຕິເຫດໜັກ</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="noFire" id="noFire" checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="noFire">ບໍ່ເຄີຍໄຟໄໝ້</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">ສົ່ງຄຳຂໍຂາຍ</button>
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-gold">ກັບຄືນ</a>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center bg-dark text-gold">
        <div class="container">
            <p>ທີ່ຢູ່: ນະຄອນຫຼວງວຽງຈັນ, ປະເທດລາວ</p>
            <p>ໂທ: +856 20 1234 5678</p>
            <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com</p>
            <p>ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາ:
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@your.tiktok" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">TikTok</a>
            </p>
            <p>ດາວໂຫຼດແອັບ:
                <a href="https://play.google.com/store" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Google Play</a> |
                <a href="https://www.apple.com/app-store/" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">App Store</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>